'''Mount Edgecombe''' is a gated community situated just north of [[Durban]], [[KwaZulu Natala]], [[Afrika Borwa|South Africa]], part of [[eThekwini|eThekwini Metropolitan Municipality]]. It was previously a sugar growing area. The population increased 89% between 2001 and 2011 from 3,874 to 7,323.<ref>http://census2001.adrianfrith.com/place/57259</ref><ref>http://census2011.adrianfrith.com/place/599052</ref> ke coastal toropo wa [[eThekwini|eThekwini Metropolitan Municipality]] ka moka

